🌿 Tumblr Themes 

Hi! All of my themes are now available on GitHub for easier access and updates.

### 📥 Installation
1. Choose a theme 
2. Open the theme file  
3. Copy the full code  
4. Go to your Tumblr → **Edit Theme → Edit HTML**  
5. Paste the code and save  

